ings  top positions mcclain value management llc overview date founded  headquarters  elm street suite b new canaan ct  employees worldwide  industries investment services  portfolio management company description mcclain value managements investment strategies include select value core valueand small cap value these strategies are offered as actively managed discretionary accounts each strategy employs a concentrated outoffavor valuebased investment approach mcclain creates longterm valuebased portfolios that invest in publiclytraded stocks the firms allcap strategies core value and select value differ primarily in risk tolerance sector diversification and the number of stocks in each portfolio mcclains small cap value strategy is similar to their select value strategy except for a limitation on the size of the companies and a difference in the number of stocks held stock overlap exists among all three products within each of the strategies all accounts are managed alike except with respect to any clientspecific restrictions or tax timing considerations also weightings in specific stocks may differ based on mcclains judgment of the relative merits of each stock at the time the account was initiated website httpwwwmcclainvaluecom in the news see more see full news coverage and complete stories with relsci professional create your news feed see more executives  employees phillip crandall mcclain founder  managing partner joseph wilkins donaldson managing partner lilly chi chief compliance officer jean a curtis research analyst see our list of current and previous employees when you upgrade start my free trial ➤ see more paths to mcclain value management llc mcclain value management llc you connections via relationship science mcclain value management llc sync your contacts to see how you can connect with mcclain value management llc start my free trial ➤ see more holdings  top positions restricted data only for relsci professional users start my free trial ➤ see more