 value management llc snapshot people company overview mcclain value management llc is an employee owned investment manager the firm provides its services to individuals high net worth individuals pension and profit sharing plans pooled investment vehicles charitable organizations corporations state or municipal government entities trusts foundations and endowments it manages separate clientfocused equity portfolios the firm invests in the equity markets of the united states it typically invests in the value stocks of small cap and all cap companies the firm employs a fundamental analysis with a bottomup stock picking approach to create its equity portfolios it benchmarks the performance of its equity portfolios against the sp mcclain value management llc is an employee owned investment manager the firm provides its services to individuals high net worth individuals pension and profit sharing plans pooled investment vehicles charitable organizations corporations state or municipal government entities trusts foundations and endowments it manages separate clientfocused equity portfolios the firm invests in the equity markets of the united states it typically invests in the value stocks of small cap and all cap companies the firm employs a fundamental analysis with a bottomup stock picking approach to create its equity portfolios it benchmarks the performance of its equity portfolios against the sp  index russell  index and russell  value index the firm conducts inhouse research to make its investments mcclain value management llc was founded in  and is based in new canaan connecticut detailed description  elm streetsuite bnew canaan ct united statesfounded in  phone  fax  wwwmcclainvaluecom key executives for mcclain value management llc mr phillip crandall mcclain cfa managing partner and chief compliance officer ms lillian chi operations manager mr joseph wilkins donaldson managing partner ms jean a curtis research analyst compensation as of fiscal year  similar pri